query:
UPDATE
                    address 
                SET
                    country = COALESCE($1, country),
                    region = COALESCE($2, region),
                    city = COALESCE($3, city),
                    street = COALESCE($4, street),
                    postal_code = COALESCE($5, postal_code),
                    street_number = COALESCE($6, street_number)
                WHERE
                    company_id = $7;
